ries caused by gunshot and chemical weapons). Medical practitioners and first-aiders are also threatened and attacked in Hong Kong. More importantly, government-supported gang members and police officers even force first-aiders and medics not to help injured citizens. <br />\n<br />\nGiven the humanitarian crisis in Hong Kong, we call for immediate help from neutral hospital ships.<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n文宣組入: 關於醫療船<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">包含無比政治槓桿力量既呼籲!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請推 &amp; 支持: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBmdrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBmdrS</a>"},{"pid":"88a2e21fcaef9889f34dfb0128bc7185b24560e0","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fcc3ebaa10aaa84e1eee7a96edb06cf3de9d406","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:14:02.000Z","msg":"An Urgent Call for Hospital Ships<br />\n<br />\nSince June 2019, Hong Kong protesters, reporters, first aiders, medical practitioners and other citizens (including children, elderly and pregnant women) have been facing high levels of threat, excessive force and attacks from government-supported gang members and police officers who do not follow the law and orders. Hong Kong people are attacked regardless of their participation in protests (e.g., people are attacked in MTR stations; those in elderly centres and at home are also affected by the chemical weapons)<br />\n<br />\nThe local medical systems are not designed for providing combat medical services (e.g., injuries caused by gunshot and chemical weapons). Medical practitioners and first-aiders are also threatened and attacked in Hong Kong. More importantly, government-supported gang members and police officers even force first-aiders and medics not to help injured citizens.<br />\n<br />\nGiven the humanitarian crisis in Hong Kong, we call for immediate help from neutral hospital ships.<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n文宣組入: 關於醫療船<br />\n<br />\n包含無比政治槓桿力量既呼籲!!!<br />\n<br />\n請推 &amp; 支持:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBmdrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBmdrS</a>"},{"pid":"9256c7e5f50e2fb2f959610cd4306ceaa2d48a99","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"其實藍絲好純真，要佢地支持可能比想像中易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438639</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9cada9acb969fdd4805f33b2f4181db58bab9294","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"又要推返呢個post上來"},{"pid":"160d2bb462ef80966023b6b0b0ac731fa350ea4a","tid":1438780,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"5d3f93ae431b7157dc60fe7d4610ce5e57571ca8","tid":1438780,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7c8b276f19d45ed17ee2faf107888c8a70c85840","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"邀請美軍-總統已出聲警告中國，我哋準備1000支美國國旗助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469834</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e857e8d4c9352ab1097affb6e9f117aff232587f","tid":1438780,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ca6f76cfcaf9d7485514981d004b840f533423","tid":1438780,"uid":40826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路"},{"pid":"076d8f3246360fd2f89d5827c90918d3ebc3c322","tid":1438780,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:54:1